commit.message:
Merge pull request #1 from Detry322/patch-1

Add more cross-platform ignores.
Set session['rooms'] on openStream if needed.

Fix race condition when switching topics.
Boost to 5 possible random twitter auths.
Allow bigger range for neutral classification.
Add ability to change tracking query.
